data.description: Don't miss out on this exceptional Chatham property - it's a true gem that won't stay on the market for long! This well-maintained two-unit home also features a fantastic bonus: an "In-Law Suite" in the basement, which comprises a one-bedroom apartment.  Whether you're an owner-occupant looking for a comfortable residence or an investor seeking a valuable property, this home is an excellent choice. Each unit boasts gleaming hardwood floors throughout, with spacious living and dining rooms that offer a welcoming and comfortable atmosphere.  Not only are these units roomy, but there's also the potential to convert them into three-bedroom apartments, providing even more versatility and value. Don't wait to seize this opportunity in Chatham - schedule your viewing today!
